Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:45.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:49.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the ever-popular segment...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:53.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Kain Hikaru's "Gowa! and Uwe~"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:55.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with the first postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:58.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"What is Grimoire Heart after?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:06.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been ordered to capture Lord \NZeref and to wipe out Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:10.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"What's Gray-san's type?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:14.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"P.S. I'd rather have more \NGray-san and less Hikaru."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:17.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, this is {\i1}my{\i0} segment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:20.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:24.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the last episode, Lucy figured out \Nthe location of Master Mavis's grave,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:26.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but Cana put her to sleep for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all "oh crap!" and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:32.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:47.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:50.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... One of \Nthe 7 Kin of Purgatory?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Cana?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:56.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Cana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:58.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:03.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know, but what does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:05.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you are going to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:12.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get separated from Cana somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:15.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And... I was asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:18.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do? I don't know what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:24.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... But I have to \Ndo something about this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:31.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can give me all the evil eye you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't scared or nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:34.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:39.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm Kain Hikaru, one of the \N7 Kin of Purgatory of Grimoire Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm powerful, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how powerful you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:47.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is that you've \Nstood against our guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:49.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you on, so come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:53.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:56.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all like, bristly here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:58.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your own hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, this guy's a piece of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:04.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:08.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you my magic, Visit at the Ox Hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the name gives me the creeps...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.06,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:17.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, hand over one of your hairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:23.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Visit at the Ox Hour needs one of your hairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:24.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:30.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stick your hair into Mr. Cursey \Nhere, I can move you exactly how I wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:33.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an extremely powerful curse magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:37.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me even less \Nlikely to give it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you just realized this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:42.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait, I've never \Nheard of magic like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:44.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's gotta be a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bluff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:51.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the doll's name is Mr. Cursey. \NWeren't you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:57.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, bluff means that you're exaggerating \Nand you can't really do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:05:00.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I never lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:05.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I just hit a nerve I shouldn't have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:08.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:11.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think so, why don't you try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:13.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:16.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my own bristle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:18.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stick it into Mr. Cursey, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:24.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A bristle is a coarse, dry hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:25.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this guy's a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:35.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you feel the extreme magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:40.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to hug it or kiss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:43.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm a little hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:47.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakdance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The llama position.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The pigeon position.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:59.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The scallop position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:03.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:06.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three embarrassing pin-up poses in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're enjoying this, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:12.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm mad now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:20.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you ask me to go out \Nwith you, it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:23.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our little tête-à-tête ends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:25.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When did we change to a soap opera?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:29.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I'm cold-hearted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to play around, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:37.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:40.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always totally serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I also get these types?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:46.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Golden Bull, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:49.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Taurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:52.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Celestial Spirit Wizard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And one of the 12 Zodiac Gates?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:59.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you attack Lucy-san with \Nthat lascivious look on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:04.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You look delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:12.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Taurus, show him what one of the strongest \NSpirits in the Spirit World can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:15.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'm gonna finish it good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:20.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He got finished good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:24.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost... in a battle of power?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:28.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That cow-looking thing's \Nmade me even hungrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:28.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:33.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:35.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's even stronger without magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's fast, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:39.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Running...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:40.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta slow him down...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:41.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:44.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Centaur, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:45.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sagittarius!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:47.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-moshimoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's a horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:51.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for his legs... Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:54.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, as it were!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:58.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, I am not a food \Nsource, as it were-moshimoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:00.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dadasturn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He kicked them back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:02.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:10.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do apologize, Lucy-dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sagittarius...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:15.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Scorpion, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorpio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:18.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:20.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:25.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm on vacation \Nwith Aquarius right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:28.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish this up quick and \Nget right back to her, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:29.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:31.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tell her I said hi, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:32.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little scared about afterwards, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On vacation with your girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:37.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not jealous in the slightest, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:39.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Buster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:46.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me some tastier Spirits \Nthan this sandy scorpion, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:50.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible? My sand was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:52.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is working!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:09:00.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If sand won't work, I don't \Nhave any reason to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:05.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:08.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Cursey still has my hair in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:12.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So if I change the material that \NMr. Cursey is made out of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:14.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It changes yourself, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Cursey, change!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From iron, to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...brightly glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:23.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining Sumo Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:33.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not look like it, but I'm one of \Nthe 7 Kin of Purgatory... I'm powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:38.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now out with something tastier!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:42.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, a Spirit like \Nthis might actually work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:44.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Lesser Dog, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:45.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nicolas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:53.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:57.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People say I'm cute, but \Nthis guy's at another level!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand him over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:04.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That made things worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:06.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cancer, handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:09.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Been a good while-ebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:10.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:14.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't call me much, so I'd thought \Nyou'd forgotten about me-ebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:17.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how would you like your hair-ebi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:20.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't get the situation, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:24.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he readying a pot \Nof boiling water-ebi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:28.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just give him such an embarrassing \Ncut he can't show his head in public!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:29.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay-ebi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:30.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ebi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:32.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ebi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:35.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Embarrassing-ebi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:37.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What-ebi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:41.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! My special scissors-ebi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:45.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My bristles aren't so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's some crazy hair-ebi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:49.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ebi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:53.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then... Please, Aries!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll try my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:01.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:04.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:09.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... I'm going to cause you trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:12.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:13.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:17.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You silly... I never thought \Nthat you... were a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:19.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:23.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I leap into your arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Into my arms? Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:30.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:34.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been such a baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:37.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We might've just met, but... I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:38.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wool Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:48.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine... Where did you \Nget such acting chops?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:49.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:51.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Aries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:56.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All men are simpletons, so you \Ncan be of help to Lucy this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:03.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is my devotion such a burden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:07.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Spirit combo's been wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:12.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:14.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, enough playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:16.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get serious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:20.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Change Mr. Cursey's material to cotton!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:25.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish you with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:28.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Change myself to iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:34.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:36.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get all upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:38.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't work on me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:40.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to pay you back for Galuna Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:43.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beating you too quickly would be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:45.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Play with me a little longer, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:49.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's way stronger than she was before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:53.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't use even half of my power back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:57.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to get crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:03.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:08.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:12.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to it, I'm saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:15.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy came flyin' in from over \Nthere... real ugly-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:18.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any other way to get sent flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:22.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kain, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:23.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultear-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:26.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:28.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, you're fighting, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:30.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's mine. You can't have her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:31.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's crazy strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Natsu's having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:37.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:38.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:41.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there are two enemies now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:45.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are two of us now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:49.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's forget we're \Nrivals in the exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:52.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll reform the team!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.74,0:13:55.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:59.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This combination brings back the memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:02.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Makes you remember the time we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:06.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:08.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:10.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:17.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're like some happy \Ncouple! How dare they!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:28.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're like some happy-go-lucky couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:30.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,2 of the 7 Kin of Purgatory...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:34.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:39.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultear-san, these people aren't \Nworth your time to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:41.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can beat them both myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:43.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just me, and I can handle them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:44.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it won't be 2 on 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, I'd rather it be 2 on 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's completely forgetting about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll leave them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:58.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take Zeref to \NMaster Hades, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:01.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You've already discovered him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:02.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:03.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them have Zeref!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's this World of Great \NMagic thing or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it'll be bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:12.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I still have to pay \Nhim back for my scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:17.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let them have 'im \N'til I punch his face in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:20.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it? Don't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:27.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel like showing them just how \Npowerful the 7 Kin of Purgatory are,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:29.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,no one can stand up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:33.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't betray your trust, Ultear-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it when it counts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:39.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Guess I'll beat this guy first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go after her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:47.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:50.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:55.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I plucked a hair when you were running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:16:02.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With that hair, you and \NMr. Cursey are now one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:05.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're now completely under my control!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:08.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:10.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:12.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:15.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like those two get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More than friends, but less than lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,None of the above!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:24.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three embarrassing pin-up poses in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:29.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're enjoying this, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:35.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy is made to move exactly like that doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:43.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like it says, it's a Lost Magic where \Nyou curse your opponent and attack them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:48.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lullaby Flute that Natsu and the \Nothers once fought is another example.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:55.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on how it's used, Kain Hikaru's \NMr. Cursey could well spell doom for the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:58.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is truly a fearsome magic, probably!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard the man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:00.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do the bunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:06.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fun for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:11.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you beat up your pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:15.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:17.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:24.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu's getting beaten up by Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:25.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're not even in Edolas...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:27.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that for, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:29.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not me doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:32.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:33.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:34.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is more annoying than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:39.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:42.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get more powerful when \Nyou're under that thing's control?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:45.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:47.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No lovey-dovey on my watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:49.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't lovey-dovey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:51.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They llllike each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:56.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna do funny business \Nwith me watching, do it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:18:00.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hug him until his bones break!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:03.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold him to the bone so \Nhe can never get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:07.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pump him so full of your \Nfeelings he flies into the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:10.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of Visit at the Ox \NHour is far more than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:13.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, tragedy will befall the two...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:14.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:16.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Cursey, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:20.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, Lucy, I stole his doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:22.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You thieving cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice going, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:24.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:38.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:42.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talons of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:46.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:48.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:50.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the opposite of how he looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:53.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast and limber!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:57.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think an official guild \Ncan actually beat Grimoire Heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:06.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:10.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't get free!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:17.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay put! I'll get Virgo to free you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:21.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:24.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've run out of magic power now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:27.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:32.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:34.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:37.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now watch as I finish her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:39.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:41.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not if I can help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:43.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, and that, and this, and that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:45.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:50.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry Natsu, Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:54.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:56.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a lot stronger than he looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:59.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle him somehow, so run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:01.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:14.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Running away by myself? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:20.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always more fun when \Nwe're together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:25.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cold-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:29.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush that cute little \Nface of yours flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:34.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm awkward, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do this right at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My body's moving on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:55.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodge him, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:57.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bending my body too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:00.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Able to move her body \Nfreely, without restraint!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Lucy is on the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:05.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, please keep my joints in mind, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:06.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This... might actually work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:14.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had an even better idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:17.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist... of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:19.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:21.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! It's not hot \Nfor the person using it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:22.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:24.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"I think," he says!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:24.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:26.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:28.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:30.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Max speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:31.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:32.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:34.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Max speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:39.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:43.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is there a reason my \Nentire body is on fire now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Move:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:50.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:57.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:22:00.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By combining Natsu's fire \Npowers with Happy's speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:04.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,through Mr. Cursey, Lucy became \Na flaming ball of magic power,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:06.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,which landed a direct hit on Kain Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:13.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.96,0:22:15.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:16.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:20.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do a victory pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:21.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.41,0:22:24.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, no more...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.46,0:23:59.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, I'm through... I can't move any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.68,0:24:01.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Suck it up, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:05.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna retire before doing anything \Nthe slightest bit productive? That's so lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.35,0:24:08.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have a knack for drilling a hole \Nright into the heart, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.83,0:24:11.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just letting everyone else \Nhave their time in the sun, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.96,0:24:13.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks a bunch for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.86,0:24:16.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Dead-End of Despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.83,0:24:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I haven't \Neven gotten serious yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.04,0:24:21.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, totally awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.75,0:24:25.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, fine, hurry up and be awesome then.
